Compiling:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/local 
make -j4 install


Other useful flags to cmake:
	-DMEOW_QT=1              - enable a qt-only build
	-DMEOW_WITH_OPUS=1       - enable opus support (needs libopusfile)
	-DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug - compile for use with gdb
	-DMEOW_PACKAGE=DEB       - `make package` will build a deb
	-DMEOW_PACKAGE=RPM       - `make package` will build an rpm

